0" end="20.030">心</span><span begin="20.030" end="20.310">も</span><span begin="20.760" end="20.970">跳</span><span begin="20.970" end="21.180">ね</span><span begin="21.180" end="21.530">上</span><span begin="21.530" end="21.700">が</span><span begin="21.700" end="21.900">っ</span><span begin="21.900" end="22.270">て</span><span begin="22.270" end="22.650">過</span><span begin="22.650" end="23.000">呼</span><span begin="23.000" end="23.600">吸</span><span begin="23.600" end="23.730">気</span><span begin="23.840" end="24.010">味</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">迟钝的内心也随之剧烈跳动 仿佛过度呼吸</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Donkan na kokoro mo haneagatte kakokyuu gimi</span></p><p begin="24.510" end="29.680" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="24.510" end="24.540">「</span><span begin="24.540" end="24.750">も</span><span begin="24.750" end="25.020">う</span><span begin="25.290" end="26.040">僕</span><span begin="26.040" end="26.130">を</span><span begin="26.250" end="26.970">守</span><span begin="26.970" end="27.160">る</span><span begin="27.550" end="27.630">も</span><span begin="27.760" end="28.030">の</span><span begin="28.280" end="28.480">は</span><span begin="28.480" end="28.650">な</span><span begin="28.650" end="28.830">い</span><span begin="28.830" end="29.050">け</span><span begin="29.050" end="29.230">れ</span><span begin="29.230" end="29.650">ど</span><span begin="29.650" end="29.680">」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">「虽然已经没有能保护我的东西了」</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">&quot;Mou boku o mamoru mono wa nai keredo&quot;</span></p><p begin="30.480" end="32.310" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="30.480" end="30.790">続</span><span begin="30.900" end="31.290">き</span><span begin="31.290" end="31.460">は</span><span begin="31.460" end="31.650">出</span><span begin="31.650" end="31.850">て</span><span begin="31.850" end="32.070">こ</span><span begin="32.070" end="32.240">な</span><span begin="32.240" end="32.310">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">却说不出接下来的话</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tsuzuki wa detekonai</span></p><p begin="32.790" end="34.620" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="32.790" end="33.060">情</span><span begin="33.170" end="33.570">景</span><span begin="33.570" end="33.680">に</span><span begin="33.680" end="34.100">彷</span><span begin="34.100" end="34.310">徨</span><span begin="34.310" end="34.620">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在情景中彷徨</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Joukei ni samayoi</span></p><p begin="35.800" end="41.690" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="35.800" end="36.180">ど</span><span begin="36.180" end="36.780">う</span><span begin="36.780" end="36.940">し</span><span begin="36.940" end="37.700">て</span><span begin="37.700" end="37.920">も</span><span begin="38.380" end="38.760">肌</span><span begin="38.760" end="38.950">を</span><span begin="38.950" end="39.180">す</span><span begin="39.180" end="39.500">り</span><span begin="39.500" end="39.660">抜</span><span begin="39.760" end="40.160">け</span><span begin="40.160" end="40.350">る</span><span begin="40.450" end="41.230">全</span><span begin="41.230" end="41.480">て</span><span begin="41.480" end="41.690">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">对那些无论如何都会从肌肤间溜走的一切</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Doushitemo hada o surinukeru subete ni</span></p><p begin="42.210" end="47.280" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="42.210" end="42.710">どう</span><span begin="42.710" end="42.940">し</span><span begin="42.940" end="43.700">て</span><span begin="43.700" end="43.910">も</span><span begin="44.400" end="45.020">別</span><span begin="45.020" end="45.550">れ</span><span begin="45.550" end="45.780">を</span><span begin="45.780" end="45.940">言</span><span begin="45.940" end="46.150">え</span><span begin="46.150" end="46.510">な</span><span begin="46.510" end="46.740">か</span><span begin="46.740" end="46.920">っ</span><span begin="46.920" end="47.280">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无论如何也说不出再见</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Doushitemo wakare o ienakatta</span></p><p begin="48.350" end="51.050" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="48.350" end="48.900">新</span><span begin="48.900" end="49.090">し</span><span begin="49.090" end="49.290">い</span><span begin="49.290" end="49.470">こ</span><span begin="49.470" end="49.640">と</span><span begin="49.640" end="50.050">始</span><span begin="50.050" end="50.200">め</span><span begin="50.200" end="50.400">る</span><span begin="50.400" end="50.810">度</span><span begin="50.810" end="51.050">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">每当开始新的事物</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Atarashii koto hajimeru tabi ni</span></p><p begin="51.560" end="54.010" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="51.560" end="51.870">内</span><span begin="51.870" end="52.280">心</span><span begin="52.280" end="52.660">誰</span><span begin="52.660" end="52.860">か</span><span begin="52.860" end="53.000">が</span><span begin="53.000" end="53.240">邪</span><span begin="53.240" end="53.420">魔</span><span begin="53.420" end="53.600">を</span><span begin="53.600" end="53.810">す</span><span begin="53.810" end="54.010">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">内心深处总有谁在阻挠</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Naishin dareka ga jama o suru</span></p><p begin="54.560" end="1:00.000" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="54.560" end="54.910">電</span><span begin="54.910" end="55.300">車</span><span begin="55.300" end="55.490">の</span><span begin="55.490" end="55.900">中</span><span begin="55.900" end="56.280">じゃ</span><span begin="56.810" end="57.170">大</span><span begin="57.170" end="57.350">人</span><span begin="57.350" end="57.530">た</span><span begin="57.530" end="57.710">ち</span><span begin="57.710" end="57.890">は</span><span begin="57.890" end="58.100">ス</span><span begin="58.100" end="58.250">マ</span><span begin="58.250" end="58.480">ホ</span><span begin="58.480" end="58.680">に</span><span begin="58.680" end="58.760">夢</span><span begin="58.870" end="59.410">中</span><span begin="59.410" end="59.630">な</span><span begin="59.630" end="59.840">の</span><span begin="59.840" end="1:00.000">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">电车里的大人们明明都沉迷于手机</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Densha no naka ja otonatachi wa sumaho ni muchuu na no ni</span></p><p begin="1:00.500" end="1:06.040" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:00.500" end="1:00.530">「</span><span begin="1:00.530" end="1:00.900">誰</span><span begin="1:00.900" end="1:01.100">も</span><span begin="1:01.100" end="1:01.480">僕</span><span begin="1:01.480" end="1:01.670">を</span><span begin="1:01.670" end="1:01.880">止</span><span begin="1:01.880" end="1:02.040">め</span><span begin="1:02.040" end="1:02.240">ら</span><span begin="1:02.240" end="1:02.420">れ</span><span begin="1:02.420" end="1:03.040">な</span><span begin="1:03.040" end="1:03.090">い</span><span begin="1:03.090" end="1:03.120">、</span><span begin="1:03.540" end="1:03.740">止</span><span begin="1:03.740" end="1:03.910">め</span><span begin="1:03.910" end="1:04.090">る</span><span begin="1:04.090" end="1:04.280">の</span><span begin="1:04.280" end="1:04.480">は</span><span begin="1:04.480" end="1:04.830">僕</span><span begin="1:04.830" end="1:05.020">自</span><span begin="1:05.020" end="1:05.410">身</span><span begin="1:05.410" end="1:06.010">だ</span><span begin="1:06.010" end="1:06.040">」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">「谁也无法阻止我 能阻止我的只有我自己」</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">&quot;Daremo boku o tomerarenai, tomeru no wa boku jishin da&quot;</span></p><p begin="1:06.510" end="1:08.540" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:06.510" end="1:06.750">そ</span><span begin="1:06.750" end="1:06.900">う</span><span begin="1:06.900" end="1:07.460">俯</span><span begin="1:07.460" end="1:07.650">き</span><span begin="1:07.650" end="1:08.250">呟</span><span begin="1:08.250" end="1:08.420">い</span><span begin="1:08.420" end="1:08.540">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我低着头这样嘟囔着</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sou utsumuki tsubuyaita</span></p><p begin="1:08.790" end="1:10.500" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:08.790" end="1:09.060">後</span><span begin="1:09.160" end="1:09.550">悔</span><span begin="1:09.550" end="1:09.690">に</span><span begin="1:09.690" end="1:10.110">彷</span><span begin="1:10.110" end="1:10.310">徨</span><span begin="1:10.310" end="1:10.500">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在后悔中彷徨</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koukai ni samayoi</span></p><p begin="1:11.790" end="1:17.790" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:11.790" end="1:12.180">ど</span><span begin="1:12.180" end="1:12.770">う</span><span begin="1:12.770" end="1:12.920">し</span><span begin="1:12.920" end="1:13.670">て</span><span begin="1:13.670" end="1:13.900">も</span><span begin="1:14.390" end="1:14.580">知</span><span begin="1:14.580" end="1:14.800">れ</span><span begin="1:14.800" end="1:15.180">な</span><span begin="1:15.180" end="1:15.550">い</span><span begin="1:15.550" end="1:15.780">こ</span><span begin="1:15.780" end="1:16.300">と</span><span begin="1:16.300" end="1:16.690">が</span><span begin="1:16.690" end="1:17.450">あ</span><span begin="1:17.450" end="1:17.790">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">总有些无论如何也无法知晓的事</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Doushitemo shirenai koto ga aru</span></p><p begin="1:18.170" end="1:23.650" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:18.170" end="1:18.800">どう</span><span begin="1:18.800" end="1:18.930">し</span><span begin="1:18.930" end="1:19.700">て</span><span begin="1:19.700" end="1:19.880">も</span><span begin="1:20.210" end="1:20.410">う</span><span begin="1:20.410" end="1:20.620">ま</span><span begin="1:20.620" end="1:20.990">く</span><span begin="1:20.990" end="1:21.190">呼</span><span begin="1:21.190" end="1:21.820">吸</span><span begin="1:21.820" end="1:22.280">が</span><span begin="1:22.280" end="1:22.550">で</span><span begin="1:22.550" end="1:23.050">き</span><span begin="1:23.050" end="1:23.310">な</span><span begin="1:23.310" end="1:23.650">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无论如何也无法顺畅地呼吸</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Doushitemo umaku kokyuu ga dekinai</span></p><p begin="1:24.140" end="1:29.070" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:24.140" end="1:24.410">リュ</span><span begin="1:24.410" end="1:24.510">ッ</span><span begin="1:24.510" end="1:24.690">ク</span><span begin="1:24.690" end="1:24.940">サ</span><span begin="1:24.940" end="1:25.090">ッ</span><span begin="1:25.090" end="1:25.280">ク</span><span begin="1:25.280" end="1:25.470">に</span><span begin="1:25.470" end="1:25.680">詰</span><span begin="1:25.680" end="1:25.880">め</span><span begin="1:25.880" end="1:25.970">た</span><span begin="1:26.250" end="1:26.440">ハ</span><span begin="1:26.440" end="1:26.620">リ</span><span begin="1:26.620" end="1:26.810">ボ</span><span begin="1:26.810" end="1:26.990">テ</span><span begin="1:26.990" end="1:27.140">の</span><span begin="1:27.140" end="1:27.920">双</span><span begin="1:27.920" end="1:28.640">眼</span><span begin="1:28.640" end="1:29.070">鏡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">塞进背包里的纸糊双筒望远镜</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ryukkusakku ni tsumeta haribote no sougankyou</span></p><p begin="1:29.730" end="1:34.560" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:29.730" end="1:30.160">彷</span><span begin="1:30.160" end="1:30.520">徨</span><span begin="1:30.520" end="1:30.750">い</span><span begin="1:30.750" end="1:31.030">歩</span><span begin="1:31.130" end="1:31.480">く</span><span begin="1:31.480" end="1:31.880">僕</span><span begin="1:31.880" end="1:32.000">ら</span><span begin="1:32.260" end="1:32.660">何</span><span begin="1:32.660" end="1:32.910">が</span><span begin="1:33.200" end="1:33.420">見</span><span begin="1:33.420" end="1:33.920">え</span><span begin="1:33.920" end="1:34.080">る</span><span begin="1:34.080" end="1:34.320">か</span><span begin="1:34.320" end="1:34.560">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">彷徨前行的我们能看到些什么呢</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Samayoi aruku bokura nani ga mieru kana</span></p><p begin="1:48.330" end="1:50.430" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:48.330" end="1:48.530">ス</span><span begin="1:48.530" end="1:48.890">ニー</span><span begin="1:48.890" end="1:49.190">カー</span><span begin="1:49.190" end="1:49.470">を</span><span begin="1:49.470" end="1:49.650">買</span><span begin="1:49.650" end="1:49.850">い</span><span begin="1:49.850" end="1:50.010">替</span><span begin="1:50.010" end="1:50.240">え</span><span begin="1:50.240" end="1:50.430">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">换了新的运动鞋</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Suniikaa o kaikaete</span></p><p begin="1:50.780" end="1:54.000" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:50.780" end="1:51.140">長</span><span begin="1:51.140" end="1:51.520">い</span><span begin="1:51.520" end="1:52.150">髪</span><span begin="1:52.150" end="1:52.470">も</span><span begin="1:52.470" end="1:52.860">バ</span><span begin="1:52.860" end="1:52.990">ッ</span><span begin="1:52.990" end="1:53.230">サ</span><span begin="1:53.230" end="1:53.390">リ</span><span begin="1:53.390" end="1:53.610">切</span><span begin="1:53.610" end="1:53.780">っ</span><span begin="1:53.780" end="1:54.000">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">长发也果断地剪掉了</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nagai kami mo bassari kitta</span></p><p begin="1:54.480" end="2:00.000" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:54.480" end="1:54.920">ショー</span><span begin="1:54.920" end="1:55.140">ト</span><span begin="1:55.140" end="1:55.360">カ</span><span begin="1:55.360" end="1:55.490">ッ</span><span begin="1:55.490" end="1:55.650">ト</span><span begin="1:55.650" end="1:55.890">で</span><span begin="1:55.890" end="1:56.030">見</span><span begin="1:56.030" end="1:56.220">る</span><span begin="1:56.220" end="1:56.420">世</span><span begin="1:56.420" end="1:56.770">界</span><span begin="1:56.770" end="1:57.170">は</span><span begin="1:57.170" end="1:57.390">何</span><span begin="1:57.390" end="1:57.530">故</span><span begin="1:57.530" end="1:57.790">か</span><span begin="1:57.790" end="1:58.120">妙</span><span begin="1:58.120" end="1:58.280">に</span><span begin="1:58.280" end="1:58.630">色</span><span begin="1:58.630" end="1:59.020">彩</span><span begin="1:59.020" end="1:59.260">が</span><span begin="1:59.260" end="1:59.420">綺</span><span begin="1:59.420" end="1:59.800">麗</span><span begin="1:59.800" end="2:00.000">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">短发视角下的世界 不知为何色彩美妙得不可思议</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shootokatto de miru sekai wa nazeka myou ni shikisai ga kirei de</span></p><p begin="2:00.520" end="2:02.610" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:00.520" end="2:00.920">思</span><span begin="2:00.920" end="2:01.140">わ</span><span begin="2:01.140" end="2:01.310">ず</span><span begin="2:01.310" end="2:01.670">口</span><span begin="2:01.670" end="2:01.940">か</span><span begin="2:01.940" end="2:02.240">ら</span><span begin="2:02.240" end="2:02.430">出</span><span begin="2:02.430" end="2:02.610">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不由自主地脱口而出</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Omowazu kuchi kara deta</span></p><p begin="2:02.970" end="2:06.020" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:02.970" end="2:03.000">「</span><span begin="2:03.000" end="2:03.160">も</span><span begin="2:03.160" end="2:03.380">う</span><span begin="2:03.380" end="2:03.710">僕</span><span begin="2:03.710" end="2:03.900">を</span><span begin="2:03.900" end="2:04.290">守</span><span begin="2:04.290" end="2:04.530">る</span><span begin="2:04.530" end="2:04.670">も</span><span begin="2:04.670" end="2:04.890">の</span><span begin="2:04.890" end="2:05.040">は</span><span begin="2:05.040" end="2:05.260">な</span><span begin="2:05.260" end="2:05.420">い</span><span begin="2:05.420" end="2:05.670">け</span><span begin="2:05.670" end="2:05.790">れ</span><span begin="2:05.790" end="2:05.990">ど</span><span begin="2:05.990" end="2:06.020">」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">「虽然已经没有能保护我的东西了」</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">&quot;Mou boku o mamoru mono wa nai keredo&quot;</span></p><p begin="2:06.460" end="2:10.520" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:06.460" end="2:06.500">「</span><span begin="2:06.500" end="2:06.740">そ</span><span begin="2:06.740" end="2:06.920">れ</span><span begin="2:06.920" end="2:07.090">で</span><span begin="2:07.300" end="2:07.670">も</span><span begin="2:07.670" end="2:07.830">い</span><span begin="2:07.830" end="2:07.990">い</span> <span begin="2:08.250" end="2:08.520">傷</span><span begin="2:08.620" end="2:08.820">つ</span><span begin="2:08.820" end="2:08.990">い</span><span begin="2:08.990" end="2:09.170">た</span><span begin="2:09.170" end="2:09.340">過</span><span begin="2:09.340" end="2:09.530">去</span><span begin="2:09.530" end="2:09.770">が</span><span begin="2:09.770" end="2:09.920">あ</span><span begin="2:09.920" end="2:10.110">る</span><span begin="2:10.110" end="2:10.330">か</span><span begin="2:10.330" end="2:10.490">ら</span><span begin="2:10.490" end="2:10.520">」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">「那样也好 因为有受过伤的过去」</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">&quot;Soredemo ii Kizutsuita kako ga aru kara&quot;</span></p><p begin="2:11.790" end="2:17.720" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:11.790" end="2:12.170">ど</span><span begin="2:12.170" end="2:12.780">う</span><span begin="2:12.780" end="2:12.920">し</span><span begin="2:12.920" end="2:13.660">て</span><span begin="2:13.660" end="2:13.920">も</span><span begin="2:14.390" end="2:14.800">別</span><span begin="2:14.800" end="2:15.180">れ</span><span begin="2:15.180" end="2:15.550">を</span><span begin="2:15.550" end="2:15.790">言</span><span begin="2:15.790" end="2:16.310">え</span><span begin="2:16.310" end="2:16.650">な</span><span begin="2:16.650" end="2:17.160">か</span><span begin="2:17.160" end="2:17.460">っ</span><span begin="2:17.460" end="2:17.720">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无论如何也说不出再见</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Doushitemo wakare o ienakatta</span></p><p begin="2:18.190" end="2:23.490" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:18.190" end="2:18.800">どう</span><span begin="2:18.800" end="2:18.950">し</span><span begin="2:18.950" end="2:19.700">て</span><span begin="2:19.700" end="2:19.850">も</span><span begin="2:20.230" end="2:20.410">上</span><span begin="2:20.410" end="2:20.630">手</span><span begin="2:20.630" end="2:20.970">く</span><span begin="2:20.970" end="2:21.780">涙</span><span begin="2:21.780" end="2:22.300">が</span><span begin="2:22.300" end="2:22.480">出</span><span begin="2:22.480" end="2:23.060">せ</span><span begin="2:23.060" end="2:23.290">な</span><span begin="2:23.290" end="2:23.490">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无论如何也无法顺利流下眼泪</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Doushitemo umaku namida ga dasenai</span></p><p begin="2:23.790" end="2:29.560" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:23.790" end="2:24.520">旅</span><span begin="2:24.520" end="2:24.780">立</span><span begin="2:24.780" end="2:24.990">つ</span><span begin="2:25.320" end="2:26.060">僕</span><span begin="2:26.060" end="2:26.270">に</span><span begin="2:26.270" end="2:26.440">は</span><span begin="2:26.810" end="2:27.140">ど</span><span begin="2:27.140" end="2:27.540">う</span><span begin="2:27.540" end="2:27.800">に</span><span begin="2:27.800" end="2:28.310">も</span><span begin="2:28.310" end="2:28.530">言</span><span begin="2:28.530" end="2:29.020">え</span><span begin="2:29.020" end="2:29.320">な</span><span begin="2:29.320" end="2:29.560">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">对于踏上旅途的我来说无论如何也说不出口</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tabidatsu boku ni wa dounimo ienai</span></p><p begin="2:29.970" end="2:32.160" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:29.970" end="2:30.320">霞</span><span begin="2:30.320" end="2:30.540">ん</sp