</span><span begin="2:59.070" end="3:00.050">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">感到孤立无援 连阳光都显得有些碍事</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kokorobosoku natte hi no akari ga jama o suru</span></p><p begin="3:00.390" end="3:03.370" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:00.390" end="3:00.550">ポ</span><span begin="3:00.550" end="3:00.740">ケ</span><span begin="3:00.740" end="3:00.930">ッ</span><span begin="3:00.930" end="3:01.120">ト</span><span begin="3:01.120" end="3:01.300">の</span><span begin="3:01.300" end="3:01.480">チョ</span><span begin="3:01.480" end="3:01.690">コ</span><span begin="3:01.690" end="3:02.040">レー</span><span begin="3:02.040" end="3:02.240">ト</span><span begin="3:02.240" end="3:02.430">は</span><span begin="3:02.430" end="3:02.600">無</span><span begin="3:02.600" end="3:02.810">く</span><span begin="3:02.810" end="3:02.960">な</span><span begin="3:02.960" end="3:03.180">っ</span><span begin="3:03.180" end="3:03.370">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">口袋里的巧克力也吃完了</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Poketto no chokoreeto wa nakunatte</span></p><p begin="3:03.700" end="3:06.380" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:03.700" end="3:03.960">不</span><span begin="3:03.960" end="3:04.310">安</span><span begin="3:04.310" end="3:04.510">ば</span><span begin="3:04.510" end="3:04.870">か</span><span begin="3:04.870" end="3:05.080">り</span><span begin="3:05.080" end="3:05.310">が</span><span begin="3:05.420" end="3:05.800">連</span><span begin="3:05.800" end="3:05.980">な</span><span begin="3:05.980" end="3:06.170">っ</span><span begin="3:06.170" end="3:06.380">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只剩下接连不断的不安</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Fuan bakari ga tsuranatta</span></p><p begin="3:08.030" end="3:12.050" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:08.030" end="3:08.400">電</span><span begin="3:08.400" end="3:08.790">車</span><span begin="3:08.790" end="3:08.970">を</span><span begin="3:08.970" end="3:09.150">降</span><span begin="3:09.150" end="3:09.240">り</span><span begin="3:09.340" end="3:09.550">た</span><span begin="3:09.550" end="3:09.860">ら</span><span begin="3:10.290" end="3:10.460">知</span><span begin="3:10.460" end="3:10.660">ら</span><span begin="3:10.660" end="3:10.770">な</span><span begin="3:10.770" end="3:10.920">い</span><span begin="3:11.020" end="3:11.420">世</span><span begin="3:11.420" end="3:11.830">界</span><span begin="3:11.830" end="3:12.050">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">下了电车便是未知的世界</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Densha o oritara shiranai sekai de</span></p><p begin="3:12.490" end="3:18.030" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:12.490" end="3:12.520">「</span><span begin="3:12.520" end="3:12.750">そ</span><span begin="3:12.750" end="3:12.920">れ</span><span begin="3:12.920" end="3:13.160">で</span><span begin="3:13.290" end="3:13.640">も</span><span begin="3:13.640" end="3:13.800">い</span><span begin="3:13.800" end="3:13.970">い</span> <span begin="3:14.210" end="3:14.590">寂</span><span begin="3:14.590" end="3:15.040">し</span><span begin="3:15.140" end="3:15.380">さ</span><span begin="3:15.380" end="3:15.510">は</span><span begin="3:15.750" end="3:16.130">思</span><span begin="3:16.130" end="3:16.640">い</span><span begin="3:16.640" end="3:16.750">出</span><span begin="3:16.870" end="3:17.240">と</span><span begin="3:17.240" end="3:17.420">な</span><span begin="3:17.420" end="3:17.610">る</span><span begin="3:17.610" end="3:17.800">か</span><span begin="3:17.800" end="3:18.000">ら</span><span begin="3:18.000" end="3:18.030">」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">「那样也好 因为寂寞终将化作回忆」</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">&quot;Soredemo ii Sabishisa wa omoide to naru kara&quot;</span></p><p begin="3:18.520" end="3:23.330" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:18.520" end="3:18.740">変</span><span begin="3:18.740" end="3:18.920">わ</span><span begin="3:18.920" end="3:19.080">り</span><span begin="3:19.080" end="3:19.290">ゆ</span><span begin="3:19.290" end="3:19.440">く</span><span begin="3:19.440" end="3:19.700">自</span><span begin="3:19.700" end="3:20.090">分</span><span begin="3:20.090" end="3:20.240">に</span><span begin="3:20.640" end="3:20.820">ま</span><span begin="3:20.820" end="3:20.970">だ</span><span begin="3:20.970" end="3:21.370">初</span><span begin="3:21.370" end="3:21.570">め</span><span begin="3:21.570" end="3:21.800">ま</span><span begin="3:21.800" end="3:21.930">し</span><span begin="3:21.930" end="3:22.150">て</span><span begin="3:22.150" end="3:22.480">が</span><span begin="3:22.480" end="3:22.660">言</span><span begin="3:22.660" end="3:22.870">え</span><span begin="3:22.870" end="3:23.080">な</span><span begin="3:23.080" end="3:23.330">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">还无法对不断改变的自己说出那句初次见面</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kawariyuku jibun ni mada hajimemashite ga ienai</span></p><p begin="3:24.490" end="3:27.010" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:24.490" end="3:24.920">運</span><span begin="3:24.920" end="3:25.290">命</span><span begin="3:25.290" end="3:25.490">を</span><span begin="3:25.490" end="3:25.750">妄</span><span begin="3:25.850" end="3:26.230">想</span><span begin="3:26.230" end="3:26.450">と</span><span begin="3:26.450" end="3:26.640">呼</span><span begin="3:26.640" end="3:26.810">ん</span><span begin="3:26.810" end="3:27.010">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">将命运称作妄想</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Unmei o mousou to yonde</span></p><p begin="3:27.490" end="3:30.020" itunes:key="L39" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:27.490" end="3:27.900">別</span><span begin="3:27.900" end="3:28.140">れ</span><span begin="3:28.140" end="3:28.280">を</span><span begin="3:28.280" end="3:28.660">悪</span><span begin="3:28.660" end="3:29.060">戯</span><span begin="3:29.060" end="3:29.210">と</span><span begin="3:29.210" end="3:29.630">笑</span><span begin="3:29.630" end="3:29.800">っ</span><span begin="3:29.800" end="3:30.020">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">把离别笑作恶作剧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Wakare o itazura to waratta</span></p><p begin="3:30.510" end="3:32.890" itunes:key="L40" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:30.510" end="3:31.160">培</span><span begin="3:31.160" end="3:31.290">っ</span><span begin="3:31.290" end="3:31.490">た</span><span begin="3:31.490" end="3:31.850">人</span><span begin="3:31.850" end="3:32.220">生</span><span begin="3:32.220" end="3:32.400">を</span><span begin="3:32.400" end="3:32.620">置</span><span begin="3:32.620" end="3:32.780">い</span><span begin="3:32.780" end="3:32.890">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">放下至今培育的人生</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tsuchikatta jinsei o oite</span></p><p begin="3:32.960" end="3:35.710" itunes:key="L41" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:32.960" end="3:33.160">見</span><span begin="3:33.160" end="3:33.420">た</span><span begin="3:33.420" end="3:33.530">い</span><span begin="3:33.530" end="3:33.760">も</span><span begin="3:33.760" end="3:34.130">の</span><span begin="3:34.130" end="3:34.490">を</span><span begin="3:34.490" end="3:34.690">見</span><span begin="3:34.690" end="3:35.040">る</span><span begin="3:35.040" end="3:35.290">ん</span><span begin="3:35.290" end="3:35.710">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">去看看想要看的东西吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mitai mono o mirunda</span></p><p begin="3:36.490" end="3:39.010" itunes:key="L42" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:36.490" end="3:36.760">ス</span><span begin="3:36.760" end="3:37.130">ニー</span><span begin="3:37.130" end="3:37.510">カー</span><span begin="3:37.510" end="3:37.860">も</span><span begin="3:37.860" end="3:38.240">長</span><span begin="3:38.240" end="3:38.400">い</span><span begin="3:38.400" end="3:38.820">髪</span><span begin="3:38.820" end="3:39.010">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">运动鞋也好 长发也罢</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Suniikaa mo nagai kami mo</span></p><p begin="3:39.360" end="3:42.030" itunes:key="L43" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:39.360" end="3:39.550">自</span><span begin="3:39.550" end="3:39.890">分</span><span begin="3:39.890" end="3:40.130">さ</span><span begin="3:40.130" end="3:40.310">え</span><span begin="3:40.310" end="3:40.490">不</span><span begin="3:40.490" end="3:40.850">確</span><span begin="3:40.850" end="3:41.040">か</span><span begin="3:41.040" end="3:41.230">な</span><span begin="3:41.230" end="3:41.420">ま</span><span begin="3:41.420" end="3:41.820">ま</span><span begin="3:41.820" end="3:42.030">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">连自己都依然是不确定的状态</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Jibun sae futashika na mama de</span></p><p begin="3:42.550" end="3:44.660" itunes:key="L44" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:42.550" end="3:42.930">何</span><span begin="3:42.930" end="3:43.190">と</span><span begin="3:43.290" end="3:43.650">出</span><span begin="3:43.650" end="3:43.910">会</span><span begin="3:43.910" end="3:44.040">う</span><span begin="3:44.040" end="3:44.440">か</span><span begin="3:44.440" end="3:44.660">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">会和什么相遇呢</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nani to deau kana</span></p><p begin="3:44.760" end="3:49.600" itunes:key="L45" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:44.760" end="3:45.150">生</span><span begin="3:45.150" end="3:45.560">涯</span><span begin="3:45.560" end="3:45.720">を</span><span begin="3:45.720" end="3:46.120">流</span><span begin="3:46.120" end="3:46.320">離</span><span begin="3:46.320" end="3:46.600">い</span> <span begin="3:47.840" end="3:48.250">永</span><span begin="3:48.250" end="3:48.560">遠</span><span begin="3:48.560" end="3:48.730">を</span><span begin="3:48.730" end="3:49.150">彷</span><span begin="3:49.150" end="3:49.370">徨</span><span begin="3:49.370" end="3:49.600">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">流浪一生 永远彷徨</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shougai o sasurai eien o samayoi</span></p><p begin="4:01.300" end="4:06.860" itunes:key="L46" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:01.300" end="4:01.700">ど</span><span begin="4:01.700" end="4:02.270">う</span><span begin="4:02.270" end="4:02.420">し</span><span begin="4:02.420" end="4:03.180">て</span><span begin="4:03.180" end="4:03.380">も</span><span begin="4:03.870" end="4:04.120">世</span><span begin="4:04.120" end="4:05.070">界</span><span begin="4:05.070" end="4:05.410">を</span><span begin="4:05.410" end="4:05.540">見</span><span begin="4:05.640" end="4:05.890">た</span><span begin="4:06.000" end="4:06.200">か</span><span begin="4:06.200" end="4:06.390">っ</span><span begin="4:06.390" end="4:06.860">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无论如何都想看看这个世界</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Doushitemo sekai o mitakatta</span></p><p begin="4:07.290" end="4:13.510" itunes:key="L47" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:07.290" end="4:07.650">ど</span><span begin="4:07.650" end="4:08.250">う</span><span begin="4:08.250" end="4:08.410">し</span><span begin="4:08.410" end="4:09.180">て</span><span begin="4:09.180" end="4:09.370">も</span><span begin="4:09.910" end="4:10.140">世</span><span begin="4:10.140" end="4:11.050">界</span><span begin="4:11.050" end="4:11.210">を</span><span begin="4:11.210" end="4:11.460">知</span><span begin="4:11.460" end="4:11.640">り</span><span begin="4:11.640" end="4:12.010">た</span><span begin="4:12.010" end="4:12.230">か</span><span begin="4:12.230" end="4:12.400">っ</span><span begin="4:12.400" end="4:13.510">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无论如何都想了解这个世界</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Doushitemo sekai o shiritakatta</span></p></div></body></tt>